Git shortcut commands for common operations.

Usage:
  omni git [command]

Available Commands:
  amend        Amend last commit without editing
  blame-line   Blame specific line range
  branch-clean Delete merged branches
  diff-words   Word-level diff
  fetch-all    Fetch all remotes with prune
  log-graph    Pretty log with graph
  pull-rebase  Pull with rebase
  push         Push to remote
  quick-commit Stage all and commit
  stash-staged Stash only staged changes
  status       Short status
  undo         Undo last commit (soft reset)

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for git

Global Flags:
      --json    output as JSON
      --table   output as aligned table

Use "omni git [command] --help" for more information about a command.
